                        <interp inst="t18460105-name-405" type="given" value="ABRAHAM"></interp>ABRAHAM SIMMONDS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the service of Mr. Henry Cox, a cheese<lb></lb>monger. I know this lard and cheese by marks on them—they are my master's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Beasley's Defence.</hi> I had carried the bag about five minutes when the officer took me; I received it of Heawood and the other.</p>
